Titolo: Romance of the Three Kingdoms III: Dragon of Destiny

Anno: 1992

Descrizione: Romance of the Three Kingdoms III: Dragon of Destiny is the third in the Romance of the Three Kingdoms series of turn-based strategy games produced by Koei and based on the historical novel Romance of the Three Kingdoms. This version was released in Asia and North America for the PC, Super Nintendo Entertainment System and Mega Drive/Genesis. It is also the only  SNES game to be fully translated into Chinese.